$vim demo.pem

Add the downloaded keygen.pem file from the aws account
$chmod 400 demo.pem
$ssh -i demo.pem ec2-user@10.100.1.250    // ssh -i <file-name> ec2-user@<private-ip>

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Another method to get in to private instance through private key

$vim private.ppk
$chmod 700 private.ppk
$ssh -i private.ppk ec2-user@<ip-address> 
